&lt;LI&gt;Reduced power consumption: 4.5W (size 1), 7W (size 2), 10.5W (size 3)
&lt;LI&gt;Port size: 1/8 to 3/8 inch
&lt;LI&gt;IP65 enclosure
&lt;LI&gt;UL94V-0 conformed flame resistant mold coil material&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

